Package presenter

Class CedricArtPresenter

java.lang.Object
presenter.CedricArtPresenter
public class CedricArtPresenter extends Object
Presenter class for Cedric Art API. This class provides methods to interact with the Cedric Art API and retrieve data about artists, artworks, exhibitions, and partners.
